    import {iVXioInputEnhancer} from 'ivx-js/modules/data/ivx-io/enhancer.inputs.js'
    public class | source

    iVXioInputEnhancer

    Enhances input data from previous versions of these iVXjs settings to work with the most current version of iVXjs's input state. The previous version had two distinct input states -- Single and Multiple Input State -- which had different displays. iVXjs has only one so this will enhance by the type of input state as previously defined.
